{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ŋono no yini?","output":"What is this?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ay no yini?","output":"What is it?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Tiyai no dhi?","output":"Who is going?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Kateku no dhi?","output":"Who died?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Nja ŋono no ngandi dhi?","output":"Whose food is this?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ŋo tidhe kümü no andini?","output":"Why are you finding wealth?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ndi kanangele no andini?","output":"Why did they run?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Gbulu kanele no andini?","output":"Why did ice melt?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ŋo tidhii no yongo?","output":"When are you coming?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Kese kavoto no yongo?","output":"When did the bike spoil?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ay kamati no yongo?","output":"When did it happen?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Mva no aka?","output":"Where is the knife?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Kajamini no aka?","output":"Where are the utensils?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"No nga?","output":"Is which?"}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Anga?","output":"Which one? (colloquial)"}
